      </statement>
      <feedback>
      <p>Not Correct! </p>
    </feedback>
      </choice>
      <choice correct="no"><statement>
        <p>The red LED indicates a normal air quality and the blue LED indicates a poor air quality.</p>
      </statement>
      <feedback>
      <p>Not Correct! </p>
    </feedback>
      </choice>
      <choice correct="yes"><statement>
        <p>The positive pin of the buzzer is connected to pin 10 of the Arduino.</p>
      </statement>
      <feedback>
      <p>Correct!</p>
    </feedback>
      </choice>
      <choice correct="no"><statement>
